{"tid":1121065,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"GB Studio 讓你自製 Game Boy 遊戲","createTime":"2019-04-23T05:44:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-13T23:51:01.000Z","uid":134437,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"32efff1ff197e90bd90c763ae444278066ab9044","tid":1121065,"uid":134437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T05:44:40.000Z","msg":"甚至可以匯出到 Windows、Mac、Linux 和手機瀏覽器的模擬器上玩<br />\n <br />\nEric Chan<br />\n1 小時前<br />\n趁著 Game Boy 三十週年的雅興，大家有沒有在床下的深處挖出這台古早手提遊戲機懷念一番呢？雖說老時候的遊戲至今還是有其滋味，但人還是想要新鮮感，GB Studio 就是一個能讓你簡單自創 Game Boy 遊戲的工具，在這裡要感謝一下開發者 Chris Maltby 吧。<br />\n<br />\n受惠於 Electron 應用程式的關係，GB Studio 不需要有編程知識，只要設計一些 PNG 圖檔、透過 GBT Player 創作的音樂，就可以組成一個在 Game Boy 環境中運作的 2D 小遊戲，甚至可以匯出到 Windows、Mac、Linux 和手機瀏覽器的模擬器上玩，有興趣的朋友可以趁著長假期動動手啊。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://chinese.engadget.com/2019/04/23/gameboy-gbstudio-rom-game-builder/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchinese.engadget.com%2F2019%2F04%2F23%2Fgameboy-gbstudio-rom-game-builder%2F&d=%2FIqeUsS3N0qecbTP5cC9ONG7VHCXrvZUts5J42m7pqo%3D&h=218a0999\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://chinese.engadget.com/2019/04/23/gameboy-gbstudio-rom-game-builder/</a>"},{"pid":"f7273c811d2038bfd30a2780c36ac2b5eeb20923","tid":1121065,"uid":234134,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T06:00:30.000Z","msg":"正正正"},{"pid":"04e43c3a30434dfaec5c69fdf273bde85c2b43dd","tid":1121065,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T23:51:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A3SyeRg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA3SyeRg.png&h=31e8c04c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ViseJKB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FViseJKB.png&h=b23c4a06&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/syjQg4C.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsyjQg4C.png&h=1fed9160&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}